description:
In this episode, we explore the lives of John Wesley and George Whitefield – two men that had great impact on Christianity throughout the world, and truly dedicated their lives to the bible. George Whitefield would be instrumental in the First Great Awakening in America, where he became the best-known name on the East Coast. John Wesley on the other hand, stayed in England and led a revival that some say saved the country from a revolution.

To find out more information about John Wesley and George Whitefield, visit our website to read our extended article.
